Yeah, actually I was a psychological operations specialist in the Army.  Creating &quot;propaganda&quot;, if you'd like to call it that, was my job for four years.  I helped create the &quot;propoganda&quot; during the NATO actions on Yugoslavia.  I helped analyze the propaganda coming out of Yugoslavia as well.  (Incedentally, they were waaaaayyyy better at it than we could ever have hoped to be).  I did the same thing in Bosnia...oh and I worked on some missions in Africa too.  I know all about how propaganda works.<br>
